	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				汉堡店Shake Shack同样也是她的作品。
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p>地图设计也能玩出新花样吗？Paula Scher 是 Pentagram 的设计师之一，过去的几年里，<a href="http://www.fastcodesign.com/3056162/how-pentagrams-paula-scher-makes-a-map/9">她手绘了许多地图</a>，与那些准确、实用功能强的地图不同，“我的地图不是为了表现精确，是为了表达情感”。</p><p>Paula 觉得数据不仅仅是存在和不存在的问题，还是“选中”或“未被选中”的问题。她查阅了大量的数据，例如民航飞机的飞行线路，气候温度变化、 州际公路线路、城市间的驾驶时间和里程、房地产价格的中位数， ZIP 代码和区号等等，并把它们画到了地图上。每张地图都被狂热的标签和数据填满。</p><p>上个月，她的这些作品在&nbsp;<a href="http://brycewolkowitz.com/h/exhibition_images.php?e=64">Bryce Wolfowitz Gallery</a>&nbsp;画廊展出。</p><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/b19c845f95dc.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">这系列作品均名为 U.S. Distances</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/577877db9c1b.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">位于&nbsp; Bryce Wolfowitz Gallery 的展览</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/7f3458cf8834.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">每幅地图都展示了不同的数据</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/bdb894b29372.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/924380fc545b.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/58b7a46a45ae.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><p>说到 Paula，她的父亲是美国地质调查局的土木工程师，受父亲影响，她自幼就对地图和数据极为痴迷。“在绘制地图的时候，我感受到了很强烈的政治因素。” 今年是选举年，从各种数据上看，她感受到了南与北、东西部之间的差异。</p><p class="">Paula 目前是 Pentagram 的设计师，她完成过不少的设计，例如&nbsp;<a href="http://www.fastcodesign.com/3041777/the-untold-story-of-shake-shacks-16-billion-branding" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Shake Shack</a>&nbsp;包装,
the <a href="http://www.fastcodesign.com/3044390/innovation-engine/pentagram-rebrands-the-new-school" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">New School</a>,
 <a href="http://www.fastcodesign.com/3032629/pentagram-rebrands-philadelphias-museum-of-art-somehow-forgets-the-rocky-stairs" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Philadelphia Museum of Art</a>&nbsp;等等。<br></p><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/6315fe6e3990.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><div style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;Shake Shack 的新包装</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/a8d914c97a2b.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/9aeddb65b72c.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/94f24a0e303b.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images medium-insert-active"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/9e3783beed44.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><p style="text-align: center;">the New School 是一所设计院校，上图中的招贴广告是 Paula 设计的</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/25d6f64ab37d.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/31464bcf1d07.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/6608deac0b43.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/2dba8af9cbf6.jpg" alt="" class="">
<figcaption class=""><p>Paula 的平面设计作品，Philadelphia Museum of Art&nbsp;</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/d16f44436f3d.jpg" alt="" class="">
</figure></div><div class="com-insert-images"><figure style="margin:0;">
    <img src="/uploads/image/201603/1873cb575980.jpg" alt="">
</figure></div><p><span style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;">题图来源：</span><a href="http://www.fastcodesign.com/3056162/how-pentagrams-paula-scher-makes-a-map/2" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;">fastcodesign</a><br></p>
		</div>
	</div>
